    "faq_section_reskin_FjUHQw": {
      "type": "faq-section-reskin",
      "blocks": {
        "text_8dxAFi": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "open": true,
            "faq-question": "How do I use Counter Clean?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>To use Counter Clean, simply pour the whole 0.68 fl oz (20ml) bottle of cleaning concentrate into your Bottle for Life and slowly fill to the top (just below the neck) with tap water. Give the bottle a gentle shake to mix, then enjoy your uplifting clean!</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_jjfD6j": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "faq-question": "Which surfaces is Counter Clean suitable for?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>We're pleased to say that Counter Clean is pH neutral, which means it’s safe to use on most surfaces. That includes softer materials like aluminium, wood, stone, quartz and other sealed surfaces. We do recommend patch testing first on any particularly sensitive or precious surfaces you’re concerned about. Just spray onto a cloth and wipe a small patch to see the results. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_HxeWqT": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "faq-question": "Which surfaces is Bathroom Bliss suitable for?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>Bathroom Bliss is suitable for all the surfaces in your bathroom, including glass, mirrors, porcelain and chrome. The naturally powerful formula tackles limescale, hard water deposits and soap scum with a streak-free finish. As with Counter Clean, we recommend patch testing any particularly precious or sensitive areas first.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_qdgxrE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "faq-question": "How do I manage my membership?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>You’ll receive a new refill pack of Signature Scents refills every 90 days. You can <a href=\"/a/account/login\" title=\"Member Portal\">access your Member Portal</a> whenever you need to pause a delivery or cancel your membership. </p><p>If you have any trouble managing your membership, <a href=\"mailto:info@us.purdyandfigg.com?subject=Membership enquiry\" title=\"Member Portal\">our Customer Experience Team</a> is always on hand to help.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_j6PQrb": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "faq-question": "What's the difference between Signature & Seasonal?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>We offer two different scent collections with your Counter Clean subscription - Signature and Seasonal Scents. Our Signature Scent pack is available all year round, and contains our three best-selling scents - Uplifting Citrus, Patchouli & Cedarwood, and Grounding Vetiver. Our Seasonal Scent pack contains three limited edition new scents blended for every season. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_z6MmLP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "faq-question": "How many uses will I get out of a bottle?",
            "faq-ans": "<p>A 10.1 fl oz bottle of Counter Clean (including one 0.68 fl oz  concentrate) contains about 230 sprays. A typical household will get through one of our 10.1 fl oz bottles in two to four weeks.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
